## Test Grouping Structure

Tests are organized into tiers with distinct purposes:

| Tier | Directory | Purpose | Resource Creation |
|------|-----------|---------|-------------------|
| **Gating** | `playwright/tests/gating/` | Smoke tests, page loads, filters, navigation | None |
| **Tier 1** | `playwright/tests/tier1/` | Feature workflows requiring resource creation | Yes (VMs, namespaces) |
| **Settings** | `playwright/tests/settings/` | Serial cluster/user settings | Minimal (toggles) |
| **Non-Priv** | `playwright/tests/nonpriv/` | RBAC boundary tests | Uses pre-existing resources |
| **API** | `playwright/tests/api/` | Browserless console-proxy contract tests | Yes (via API) |

